@startuml svc-scheduling-orchestrator--post-schedule-requests

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #059669
    ParticipantBorderColor #374151
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #F9FAFB
    LifeLineBorderColor #6B7280
    BoxBorderColor #94A3B8
    BoxBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
    NoteBorderColor #64748B
    NoteBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}

header [[/microservices/svc-scheduling-orchestrator/#integration-context ⬆ svc-scheduling-orchestrator Integration Context]]

title POST /schedule-requests\nRequest optimal schedule for a trip

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-scheduling-orchestrator" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-scheduling-orchestrator/]] #DBEAFE
participant "Guide Mgmt" as GM [[/microservices/svc-guide-management/]] #E0E7FF
participant "Trail Mgmt" as TM [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/]] #FEF3C7
participant "Weather Svc" as WX [[/microservices/svc-weather/]] #F1F5F9
participant "Trip Catalog" as TC [[/microservices/svc-trip-catalog/]] #FEF3C7
participant "Notifications" as Ntfy [[/microservices/svc-notifications/]] #F1F5F9
database "PG + Valkey" as DB [[/microservices/svc-scheduling-orchestrator/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-scheduling-orchestrator.html View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /schedule-requests
activate GW #059669
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #059669

note right of Svc : Validate request body

== Cross-Service Integration ==

Svc -> GM : [[/microservices/svc-guide-management/#get-guidesguide_idavailability-get-guide-availability-windows Check guide availability]]
activate GM #E0E7FF
GM --> Svc : OK
deactivate GM

Svc -> TM : [[/microservices/svc-trail-management/#get-trailstrail_idconditions-get-current-trail-conditions Verify trail conditions]]
activate TM #FEF3C7
TM --> Svc : OK
deactivate TM

Svc -> WX : [[/microservices/svc-weather/#get-weatherforecast-get-weather-forecast Get forecast]]
activate WX #F1F5F9
WX --> Svc : OK
deactivate WX

Svc -> TC : [[/microservices/svc-trip-catalog/#get-tripstrip_id-get-trip-details Get trip details]]
activate TC #FEF3C7
TC --> Svc : OK
deactivate TC

== Database ==

Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO ...
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Created row
deactivate DB

== Async Events ==

Svc ->> Ntfy : [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#post-notifications-send-a-notification Notify assigned guides]]

Svc --> GW : 201 Created
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

@enduml